step.action:
Present findings for each repo in communication_language, using this structure:

      "📊 **Voici ce que j'ai compris sur [workspace_name] ({N} repos)** :

      **[repo_name]** (`role`) — `localPath`
      - Purpose : {what this repo seems to own}
      - Stack : {language + framework + key libs}
      - Main modules : {2–3 dominant modules or directories}
      - Contracts & execution : {key API/events/types and useful run/test clues}
      - Risks / migration : {2–3 important observations}
      - Confidence : {high|medium|low} — {main unknown if any}

      [repeat for each repo]

      {if multi-repo:}
      **Vue système**
      - {product purpose / end-to-end flow}
      - {source of truth or contract dependency}
      - {recommended repo order for a common change}

      ---
      ✅ **Tapez 'oui' pour générer les fichiers de contexte**, ou donnez vos corrections/ajouts avant que je commence."

action.action:
Spawn Task (sub-agent) with the content of step-02-arch-agent.md, substituting:
        - {{repo_name}}             = {{current_repo_name}}
        - {{repo_path}}             = {{current_repo_path}}
        - {{architect_agent_file}}  = ~/.nakiros/agents/architect.md
        - {{findings_output}}       = {{arch_findings_file}}
        - {{corrections}}           = user corrections if any, or "None"
        - {{date}}                  = today's date

step.action:
Spawn Task (sub-agent) with the content of step-03-product-agent.md, substituting:
      - {{workspace_name}}        = {workspace_name}
      - {{workspace_slug}}        = {workspace_slug}
      - {{repos_list}}            = all repos in repos_to_analyze (name + localPath, one per line)
      - {{product_agent_file}}    = ~/.nakiros/agents/product.md
      - {{findings_output}}       = {{product_findings_file}}
      - {{date}}                  = today's date
      - {{corrections}}           = user corrections if any, or "None"

check.action:
Spawn Task (sub-agent) with the content of step-04-integrator-agent.md, substituting:
        - {{workspace_name}}        = {workspace_name}
        - {{workspace_slug}}        = {workspace_slug}
        - {{repos_list}}            = all repos in repos_to_analyze (name + localPath, one per line)
        - {{findings_output}}       = {{inter_repo_findings_file}}
        - {{date}}                  = today's date
        - {{corrections}}           = user corrections if any, or "None"

step.output:
[GENERATE-CONTEXT] ✅ TERMINÉ
Per-repo :
{{for each repo: "├─ {repo}/_nakiros/architecture.md
├─ {repo}/_nakiros/stack.md
├─ {repo}/_nakiros/conventions.md
├─ {repo}/_nakiros/api.md
└─ {repo}/_nakiros/llms.txt"}}
Workspace (global) :
├─ {product_output}
